org.archive.wayback.resourceindex.cdxserver

Class AccessCheckFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.archive.wayback.resourceindex.cdxserver.AccessCheckFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CDXAccessFilter

    public class AccessCheckFilter
extends Object
implements CDXAccessFilter
    Standard CDXAccessFilter implementation useful for most cases.

    2014-11-06: Disabled per-urlkey caching of include result ( lastKey and cachedValue). It assumes exclusion is per-URL basis, which is not necessarily true (access control oracle allows for excluding captures by date-range, for example). Such optimization should be done in ExclusionFilter.

    2014-11-06: The second CDXFilter (@code cdxFilter2) is soon to be dropped. If more than one CDXFilters are needed, bundle them up in one composite CDXFilter.

      • AccessCheckFilter

        public AccessCheckFilter(AuthToken token,
                         ExclusionFilter adminFilter,
                         ExclusionFilter robotsFilter,
                         CDXFilter cdxFilter,
                         CDXFilter cdxFilter2)
        Initializes with AuthToken, two ExclusionFilters and two CDXFilters. Both cdxFilter and cdxFilter2 must pass for capture to be included (i.e. they are AND).
        Parameters:
        token - provides user privilege information
        adminFilter - administrative exclusion filter
        robotsFilter - robots exclusion filter
        cdxFilter - CDX filter for narrowing down the visible archive space.
        cdxFilter2 - Second CDX filter.
